  provinceImage3: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bd4ae5366871cfe439dbd29ec288d5d4, type: 3}
  description: "T\xE2y Ninh l\xE0 m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh thu\u1ED9c v\xF9ng \u0110\xF4ng
    Nam B\u1ED9 \u1EDF ph\xEDa Nam c\u1EE7a Vi\u1EC7t Nam, c\xF3 \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng
    bi\xEAn gi\u1EDBi gi\xE1p v\u1EDBi Campuchia. Trung t\xE2m c\u1EE7a t\u1EC9nh
    l\xE0 th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 T\xE2y Ninh. T\xE2y Ninh n\u1ED5i b\u1EADt v\u1EDBi nhi\u1EC1u
    \u0111\u1ECBa danh du l\u1ECBch v\xE0 t\xE2m linh nh\u01B0 N\xFAi B\xE0 \u0110en
    \u2013 ng\u1ECDn n\xFAi cao nh\u1EA5t Nam B\u1ED9, T\xF2a Th\xE1nh Cao \u0110\xE0i
    T\xE2y Ninh v\xE0 H\u1ED3 D\u1EA7u Ti\u1EBFng.\n\nT\xE2y Ninh c\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u
    \u0111\u1EB7c s\u1EA3n n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng nh\u01B0 B\xE1nh tr\xE1ng ph\u01A1i
    s\u01B0\u01A1ng Tr\u1EA3ng B\xE0ng, Mu\u1ED1i t\xF4m T\xE2y Ninh v\xE0 B\xF2
    t\u01A1 T\xE2y Ninh.\n\nV\u1EC1 v\u0103n h\xF3a, T\xE2y Ninh l\xE0 trung t\xE2m
    c\u1EE7a Cao \u0110\xE0i, m\u1ED9t t\xF4n gi\xE1o ra \u0111\u1EDDi t\u1EA1i Vi\u1EC7t
    Nam v\u1EDBi nhi\u1EC1u nghi l\u1EC5 v\xE0 ki\u1EBFn tr\xFAc \u0111\u1EB7c s\u1EAFc.
    C\xE1c l\u1EC5 h\u1ED9i t\xF4n gi\xE1o v\xE0 sinh ho\u1EA1t t\xEDn ng\u01B0\u1EE1ng
    t\u1EA1i T\xF2a Th\xE1nh Cao \u0110\xE0i t\u1EA1o n\xEAn n\xE9t v\u0103n h\xF3a
    t\xE2m linh ri\xEAng bi\u1EC7t c\u1EE7a v\xF9ng \u0111\u1EA5t n\xE0y."
  desSatNhap: "Theo th\xF4ng tin c\u1EADp nh\u1EADt n\u0103m 2025, t\u1EC9nh Long
    An v\xE0 T\xE2y Ninh s\xE1p nh\u1EADp th\xE0nh m\u1ED9t \u0111\u01A1n v\u1ECB
    h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh m\u1EDBi mang t\xEAn t\u1EC9nh T\xE2y Ninh, c\xF3 hi\u1EC7u
    l\u1EF1c t\u1EEB th\xE1ng 6/2025. T\u1EC9nh m\u1EDBi c\xF3 di\u1EC7n t\xEDch
    h\u01A1n 8.536km vu\xF4ng, d\xE2n s\u1ED1 h\u01A1n 3,3 tri\u1EC7u ng\u01B0\u1EDDi,
    trung t\xE2m h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh \u0111\u1EB7t t\u1EA1i TP. T\xE2n An (Long An),
    t\u1EA1o th\xE0nh v\xF9ng kinh t\u1EBF bi\xEAn gi\u1EDBi chi\u1EBFn l\u01B0\u1EE3c,
    k\u1EBFt n\u1ED1i TP.HCM v\xE0 c\u1EA3ng bi\u1EC3n."
